amplican 1.5.8
-----------------------
    o amplican has been published now, doi: 10.1101/gr.244293.118
    o clearly outperforms other tools on many benchmarks
    o please cite the paper if you ar eusing amplican

amplican 1.1.3
-----------------------
    o fixed couple bugs
    o improved HDR
    o HDR for base editors
    o example of HDR
    o FAQ vignette

amplican 1.1.2
-----------------------

    o ampliCan supports now other aligners with SAM format eg. bwa mem
    (cigarsToEvents) and pair format eg. EMBOSS needleall (pairToEvents)
    o HDR quantification
    o more then 10x speed up of extracting events from alignments

